criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years of age or older;

          -  accept EVT treatment within 6 hours of symptoms onset;

          -  In selected patients with AIS within 6 to 16 hours of last known normal who have LVO
             in the anterior circulation and meet other DAWN or DEFUSE 3 eligibility criteria..

          -  In selected patients with AIS within 6 to 24 hours of last known normal who have LVO
             in the anterior circulation and meet other DAWN eligibility criteria.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pre - onset mRS>2;

          -  severe dementia;

          -  threatening life diseases (such as malignant tumor, etc.);

          -  non acute ischemic cerebrovascular disease patients undergoing selective intravascular
             treatment;

          -  related sound window closure can not be monitoring with TCD.
